FBIS4-53238 "dreas096_c_94005" FBIS-EAS-94-096 Daily Report 18 May 1994 North Korea ROK Party Denounces DLP Chairman's Remarks ROK Party Denounces DLP Chairman's Remarks SK1805042994 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0421 GMT 18 May 94 SK1805042994 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, May 18 (KCNA) -- A spokesman for the South Korean opposition Democratic Party denounced remarks of Kim Chong-pil claiming that the "May 16 military coup" in 1961 was a "revolution", a Seoul-based radio report said. In a commentary May 14 he said the utterances of the "chairman of the Democratic Liberal Party" justifying the "May 16 military coup" which gave birth to the "Yusin" fascist dictatorship were "a mockery of history and a deception on the people".
